{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a52ab30001","title":"中央转发重工业部关于三反追赃定案经验报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a726359aee","index":0,"year":1952,"month":5,"day":10,"articleId":"a52ab30001"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"29d3804b92","type":"title","text":"中央转发重工业部关于三反追赃定案经验报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a52ab30001"},{"id":"cbca05d4ad","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a52ab30001"},{"id":"9d61642cd0","type":"appellation","text":"中央直属总党委；各中央局、分局，并转省市区党委；各大军区及志愿军党委：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a52ab30001"},{"id":"34717c81ed","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）现当三反运动进至法院审判、追赃定案的阶段，必须认真负责，实事求是，不怕麻烦，坚持到底，是者定之，错者改之，应降者降之，应升者升之，嫌疑难定者暂不处理，总之，必须做到如实地解决问题，主观主义的思想和怕麻烦的情绪，必须克服。这是共产党人统治国家的一次很好的学习，对全党和全国人民都具有很大的意义。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a52ab30001"},{"id":"47f335d081","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）兹将中央重工业部关于追赃定案艰苦斗争的经验一件发给你们，请你们加以研究，并可在党刊上发表。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a52ab30001"},{"id":"204bf57135","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央五月十日","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a52ab30001"}],"page":{"id":"818bc1a2bd","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a52ab30001","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}